{"tid":1378693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你冇發夢又係嗰一區街坊 至少撒退後落街回收物資","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T15:36:03.000Z","uid":79085,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cb965e1609b6244c36a5c20b854281c337a4d443","tid":1378693,"uid":79085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:27:34.000Z","msg":"無論你因為種種原因，怕事，怕被人拉，要返工，老豆唔比你出去，至少可以 以一個街坊身份落一落街，指路/甚至收留一下夢遊人，又或回收一下物資<br />\n<br />\n1. 你作為一個街坊係完場後落街，絕對唔犯法，而且唔洗比狗嚇，你有合理由出現係屋企樓下<br />\n2. 好多夢遊人跨區，唔識路，你大可指點下邊到安全（通常民居，木隱於林）/甚至盡地主之誼<br />\n3. 通常撒退都係電光火石，請體諒一下夢遊人會留底好多野，而且怕比屈成罪證<br />\n4. 物資真係好短缺<br />\n<br />\n如有遺留，請街坊補充<br />\n<br />\n利伸：我回收因為我愛環保，我鐘意幫人因我盡地主之誼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c60996fec987a859012538550d172bc0460b6cc","tid":1378693,"uid":168214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:27:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76b24e7cb437a7f15ce989f143570e2c084fb72e","tid":1378693,"uid":79085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:29:55.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"50495e65145471fb53a420611d5654024a3e247a","tid":1378693,"uid":79085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:32:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4af26ae8ca3bd4ea6550135c8ce6642fcea0b8c","tid":1378693,"uid":79085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:35:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1351ba6f00d1004de60ca86a8ee418e96b126235","tid":1378693,"uid":79085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:41:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4cbddd483bb58719cc04b6d87ee0d2ea620d93ba","tid":1378693,"uid":79085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:00:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef09c44c91a7e7e8ebca14e10c1a1ad70c73750c","tid":1378693,"uid":79085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:05:42.000Z","msg":"推"